title: Why is Dragon called Dazza?
body: I don't remember moving to bogan Australia

replies.body:
I would like to know what is going on here. Is this something that was accidentally shipped in the patch which was a joke? I got a little laugh the first time I noticed it, but that is all. Now it is just weird.
Also, the Vayne I played with wasn't Dazzaslayer Vayne.
Ruins the immersion.
Riot pls.
